<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Legal Notice</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        LEGAL NOTICE
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p><strong>To:</strong><br>
        {{ recipient_name }}<br>
        {{ recipient_address }}</p>
        
        <p><strong>From:</strong><br>
        {{ sender_name }}<br>
        {{ sender_address }}<br>
        Phone: {{ sender_phone }}<br>
        Email: {{ sender_email }}</p>
        
        <p><strong>Subject:</strong> {{ subject }}</p>
        
        <p>Sir/Madam,</p>
        
        <p>TAKE NOTICE that my client has instructed me to serve upon you the following legal notice:</p>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p><strong>FACTS:</strong></p>
            <p>{{ facts }}</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p><strong>DEMAND:</strong></p>
            <p>{{ demand }}</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>TAKE FURTHER NOTICE that if you fail to comply with the above demand within {{ time_limit }} from the receipt of this notice, my client will be constrained to take appropriate legal action against you including but not limited to:</p>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>{{ consequences }}</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>You are hereby called upon to comply with the above demand within the stipulated time to avoid unnecessary litigation and costs.</p>
        
        <p>This notice is served upon you under Section 80 of the Code of Civil Procedure, 1908, and other applicable provisions of law.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="date-place">
        <p>Date: {{ date }}<br>
        Place: {{ place }}</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="signature">
        <p>Yours faithfully,<br><br>
        {{ sender_name }}</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
